rows.label: qst103319_msg002
rows.name: Stop it (temp)

rows.label: qst103319_msg003
rows.name: Please capture me (temp)

rows.label: qst103319_msg004
rows.name: What to do?

rows.label: qst103319_msg005
rows.name: Help (temp)

rows.label: qst103319_msg006
rows.name: Don't help (temp)

rows.label: qst103319_msg0001
rows.name: I wonder if this woman had a family...

rows.label: qst103319_msg0002
rows.name:
If so, those left behind
must be in pain.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0101
rows.name:
I'm sorry to have you
deliver such sad news.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0201
rows.name: The body has been transported!

rows.label: qst103319_msg0202
rows.name: Thank you.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0203
rows.name: An anti-imperial organization...?

rows.label: qst103319_msg0204
rows.name:
I've only just arrived in
the capital, so I've never
heard of it... I'm sorry.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0205
rows.name: We have a clue here too!

rows.label: qst103319_msg0206
rows.name:
I've discovered fresh footprints
on top of that cliff.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0207
rows.name:
My superior went to
investigate, but... I
haven't heard anything from him.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0208
rows.name:
Would you be willing to
check on him? Please.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0209
rows.name:
Oh, yes! To get to the top of
the cliff, you'll need to open
a military-controlled gate.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0210
rows.name:
The gate is locked,
so... please take this!

rows.label: qst103319_msg0301
rows.name:
My superior is on top of the
cliff, so please check on him!
